name: Draya_Korbinari
content:
Draya Korbinari was a Human female who lived during the Galactic Civil War.
Draya Korbinari appeared as a non-player character in the video game Star Wars Galaxies, a massively multiplayer online role-playing game developed by Sony and published by LucasArts, prior to its closure on December 15, 2011.
